In this situation, `schedule.occurrences_between(start_time, end_time)` will return the correct occurrence, but adding `spans: true` will yield no results. I have opened a [PR](https://github.com/seejohnrun/ice_cube/pull/452) with a fix, but could use assistance is assessing whether this fix is appropriate.

