In debugging, I found that this [line](https://github.com/seejohnrun/ice_cube/blob/master/lib/ice_cube/validations/hour_of_day.rb#L28) was causing `time` to be moved beyond the expected occurrence result. Additionally `freq` in this context was `2` from the biweekly rule.

The [PR](https://github.com/seejohnrun/ice_cube/pull/452) has a spec to cover this situation, but again I am not convinced that my approach is best.

Any assistance is appreciated!

